OL,3,CDriver fined as dashcam shows plastic
OL,4,Cbottle lobbed from car
OL,6,FA driver has been fined #500 after
OL,7,Fbeing caught littering on another
OL,8,Fdriver's dashcam footage.
OL,10,FThe video shows a plastic bottle being
OL,11,Flobbed from a car at Bierton near
OL,12,FAylesbury, Buckinghamshire.
OL,14,FDashcam and other pictures showing
OL,15,Fsimilar incidents can now be uploaded
OL,16,Fto Buckinghamshire Council's website
OL,17,Fas part of a crackdown on the offence.
