OL,6,FThose caught throwing rubbish from
OL,7,Ftheir car will be fined and the owner
OL,8,Fof a car will be fined even if someone
OL,9,Felse has committed the offence.
OL,11,FCllr Carl Jackson, Cabinet Member for
OL,12,FEnvironment said: "I honestly can't
OL,13,Fbegin to understand what goes through
OL,14,Ftheir minds.
OL,16,F"It costs the council half a million
OL,17,Fpounds a year to clean up littering.
OL,18,FThat's six pounds a year for every
OL,19,Fman, woman and child in
OL,20,FBuckinghamshire.
