OL,3,CDriver fined as dashcam shows plastic
OL,4,Cbottle lobbed from car
OL,6,F"That's money that we don't need to
OL,7,Fspend if people just take their litter
OL,8,Fhome with them. We can invest that in
OL,9,Froads or social care instead."
OL,11,FThe money from the fines will go back
OL,12,Finto street cleaning and enforcing
OL,13,Fflytipping notices.
OL,15,FLocal litter picker, Carol Clifford
OL,16,Fsaid: "I moved into the area, I was
OL,17,Freally pleased to live in such a
OL,18,Flovely place.
