OL,3,CDriver fined as dashcam shows plastic
OL,4,Cbottle lobbed from car
OL,6,F"I became aware of the litter and I
OL,7,Fthought, if I can do something to help
OL,8,Fkeep the community clean, I'm getting
OL,9,Fmy steps in, I'm improving the
OL,10,Flocation, I'm meeting people, and I've
OL,11,Fseen other people get involved."
OL,13,FMs Clifford has previously won #250 in
OL,14,Fthe Aylesbury Litter Lotto, which
OL,15,Foffers prizes to people who show they
OL,16,Fare doing their part to keep streets
OL,17,Fclean. She donated her money for new
OL,18,Fbins.
